column5: A simple and clean space which is not only private but also affordable. 10 miles from both downtown Austin and Round Rock with easy access to I-35, you'll also be close to Dell, Samsung, Walnut Creek greenbelt, grocery, restaurants, etc. Youâ€™ll need a car in this part of town, or signed up for a rideshare. Coffee, snacks, and drinks provided. I've lived in Austin for 10 years and am happy to provide pointers for where to eat, drink, have fun, and relax.
